headline: Johnson & Johnson: No More Tears, Just Gains In Intra-Cellular Acquisition
summary: JNJ's $14B acquisition of ITCI bolsters its portfolio with Caplyta, showing strong sales and patent protection until 2033. Click here to read why JNJ is a Hold.
